Class AlbumTransferStats

java.lang.Object
  com.kallasoft.smugmug.api.json.entity.AlbumTransferStats

Class used to define an album and all the transfer statistics that can be reported for it.

Constructor Detail

AlbumTransferStats

public AlbumTransferStats(org.json.JSONObject albumObject)
                   throws IllegalArgumentException,
                          org.json.JSONException
Construct a new album transfer stat object by safely parsing all known album values (and any contained image transfer stat objects if available) out of the given JSONObject.

If a property is not available from the JSONObject, it's value is simply set to null and ignored and parsing continues.

Parameters:
albumObject - The JSONObject that will be queried for all the album transfer stats.
Throws:
IllegalArgumentException - if albumObject is null.
org.json.JSONException - if any JSONObject-related exception occurs.

Construct an object with the given album transfer stats.

Parameters:
id - The ID of the album.
bytes - The number of bytes transferred for this album.
tiny - The number of times tiny-sized images have been viewed for this album.
thumb - The number of times thumb-sized images have been viewed for this album.
small - The number of times small-sized images have been viewed for this album.
medium - The number of times medium-sized images have been viewed for this album.
large - The number of times large-sized images have been viewed for this album.
xLarge - The number of times xlarge-sized images have been viewed for this album.
x2Large - The number of times xxlarge-sized images have been viewed for this album.
x3Large - The number of times xxxlarge-sized images have been viewed for this album.
original - The number of times original-sized images have been viewed for this album.
video320 - The number of times 320-pixel sized movies have been viewed for this album.
video640 - The number of times 640-pixel sized movies have been viewed for this album.
video960 - The number of times 960-pixel sized movies have been viewed for this album.
video1280 - The number of times 1280-pixel sized movies have been viewed for this album.
imageTransferStatsList - A list of image transfer stat objects that represent the images in this album, if available.
